<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>Dm</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.    Dm                      A7
 Jyr bolyp bizge ashylshy Táńir,
.Gm            Dm
 Syryńdy maǵan aqtarshy Iem.
.   Dm                 A7
 Unattyń adam balasyn nege?
.    Gm         A7        Dm
 Mánisin munyń uqtyrshy Qudaı.

[C1]
.   Gm              F    Dm
   O, Qudaı Iem, Ózińsiń ómir.
.      Gm     A7      Dm    D7
   O, Qudaı Iem jaratqan bizdi.
.    Gm      C          C    Dm
   Bas ıip Saǵan kelip tur elim,
.     Gm       A7       Dm
   Jetelep basta shyndyqqa Isa.

[V2]
 Kúnáǵa batqan elimdi kórip,
 Jiberdiń bizge Ulyńdy jerge.
 Úzilgen úmit jalǵandy búgin,
 Máńgilik ómir syıladyń bizge.

[V3]
 Tyńdashy halqym, taımashy joldan,
 Shyndyqty jyrla Isadan alǵan.
 Shaqyrǵan bizdi shattyqa toly,
 Qazaǵym, elim, Isanyń joly.</lyrics>
